			{
				"data": {
					"id": "d90hq1zcbc80",
					"created": 1744037576560,
					"text": "xserver",
					"layout": null
				},
				"children": []
			},
			{
				"data": {
					"id": "d90hq4d73f40",
					"created": 1744037581751,
					"text": "x window system",
					"note": "X Window System被设计用于：允许多个程序共享访问同一套硬件设备。这里的硬件设备指的是《输入设备》以及《输出设备》\n\n输入设备： 鼠标，键盘\n输出设备：显卡，显示器\n\n一个叫做X Server 的程序用来实现上述的多个程序共享硬件资源的需求。X Server用来管理硬件资源的分配和使用给多个程序\n",
					"hyperlink": "http://www.x.org/releases/current/doc/",
					"hyperlinkTitle": "wiki",
					"expandState": "expand",
					"layout": null
				},
				"children": [
					{
						"data": {
							"id": "d9274jj3qyo0",
							"created": 1744210799563,
							"text": "C/S架构",
							"expandState": "expand",
							"layout": null
						},
						"children": [
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927qsz854g0",
									"created": 1744212544140,
									"text": "communication-channel",
									"note": "1. 基于TCP：因为x协议没有提供重排和重发数据包\n\n2. message：发送的消息类型被X11 协议所规定",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"data": {
							"id": "d927bscobp40",
							"created": 1744211367314,
							"text": "输入",
							"expandState": "collapse",
							"layout": null
						},
						"children": [
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927bvj7elk0",
