							"layout": null
						},
						"children": []
					},
					{
						"data": {
							"id": "d927dmn93uo0",
							"created": 1744211511622,
							"text": "窗口系统对象",
							"layout": null
						},
						"children": [
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927dqytay80",
									"created": 1744211521028,
									"text": "Windows",
									"note": "只是屏幕上一块可以绘制的区域。\n\n1. 树状层次组织起windows的\n2. root window是xserver创建的，覆盖整个屏幕，生命周期就是xserver\n3. 树结构中同层级窗口是stack order的，可以相互堆叠\n",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							},
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927dsw6p4w0",
									"created": 1744211525222,
									"text": "Pixmaps",
									"note": "也是一个支持绘制的区域。和windows不同的是。不属于树状层次结构中，并且不是直接显示在屏幕上。pixmap的内容是通过间接拷贝到windows上进行显示的。pixmap的可能存放在：系统内存，显卡的显存中，共享内存中",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							},
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927duesyag0",
									"created": 1744211528525,
									"text": "Widgets",
									"note": "应用级别的元素：按钮，菜单，文本框等。用于和用户交互。显示和事件处理的集合",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							},
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927dx2gmgo0",
									"created": 1744211534309,
									"text": "XIDs",
									"note": "资源ID，被xserver管理的资源\n\n资源：connection，windows，pixmap，cursor\n\n可通过xid实现不同client互相操作和访问",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							},
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927e0svc3c0",
									"created": 1744211542436,
									"text": "Atoms",
									"note": "为了减少x客户端和服务器之间的字符串重传。存在一个映射表。atoms代表了x协议中的一个操作",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							},
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927e29muzk0",
									"created": 1744211545627,
									"text": "Properties",
									"note": "一个键值对\n\nkey：文本字符串，代表一个atom\nvalue：atom/integer/...\n\n最初版本的属性集定义在ICCCM中，之后被扩展EWMH\n\n",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							},
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927e4isqw80",
									"created": 1744211550534,
									"text": "Grabs",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							},
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d927e6dqatk0",
									"created": 1744211554581,
									"text": "Selections，cut-copy-paste",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"data": {
							"id": "d9285ticghs0",
							"created": 1744213720759,
							"text": "扩展系统",
							"layout": null
						},
						"children": [
							{
								"data": {
									"id": "d92mvmmkpj40",
									"created": 1744255238784,
									"text": "XRandR",
									"note": "xrandr其实是X11服务器 X.Org Server 提供的XRandR(Rotate and Resize)扩展的客户端工具，它通过调用XRandR扩展接口获取所有显示相关的信息。\n\n\n显示器硬件(EDID)\n        ↑\n  通过DDC通道\n        ↑\nLinux内核 显卡驱动 (DRM/KMS，e.g. modesetting、amdgpu)\n        ↑\n      X server\n        ↑\n    XRandR扩展\n        ↑\n      xrandr命令\n      \n\n",
									"layout": null
								},
								"children": []
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"data": {
							"id": "d9p1ayxv9pk0",
							"created": 1746530255637,
							"text": "协议文档(Protocal)",
							"hyperlink": "https://x.org/releases/current/doc/xproto/x11protocol.html#x11protocol",
							"hyperlinkTitle": "x11协议",
							"layout": null
						},
						"children": [
